{"word":"H4982 - מַתְּנַי - Mattᵉnay - mat-ten-ah'ee - Mattenai","slug":"H4982","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַתְּנַי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Mattᵉnay"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mat-ten-ah'ee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Mattenai"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>מתּני</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>mattenay</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>mat-ten-ah'ee</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Mattenai = \"gift of Jehovah\" <ol><li>a priest, son of Joiarib, in the time of Joiakim</li><li>an Israelite who had and put away his foreign wife in the time of Ezra</li><li>another Israelite who had and put away his foreign wife in the time of Ezra</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H4976\">H4976</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4976\">H4976</a>, <a href=\"#/H4977\">H4977</a>, <a href=\"#/H4979\">H4979</a>, <a href=\"#/H4980\">H4980</a>, <a href=\"#/H4983\">H4983</a>, <a href=\"#/H4991\">H4991</a>, <a href=\"#/H4992\">H4992</a>, <a href=\"#/H4993\">H4993</a>, <a href=\"#/H5411\">H5411</a>, <a href=\"#/H5414\">H5414</a>, <a href=\"#/H5416\">H5416</a>, <a href=\"#/H5417\">H5417</a>, <a href=\"#/H5418\">H5418</a>, <a href=\"#/H5419\">H5419</a>"}]}